#rstats ?: how to pipe a model to augment() 

Worked in 2018
df %>% 
do(fit =  lm(x_1 ~  x_2, data = .)) %>% 
augment(fit)

Works now but do() is deprecated
df %>% 
do(fit = lm(x_1 ~ x_2,  data = .)) %>% 
mutate(new = map(fit, augment))
